Angular 1.3 Restaurant App

The Application is basically Restaurant App using Angular and Bootstrap

It includes the Some of the Core Angular Concepts

Scope
Directives
Controllers
Services and Factories
Communication using $resource and promises
Filters
Responsive web design

//How to run this project using JSON-Server
--> Install json-server using Node Package Manager(NPM)
--> Run npm install json-server -g
--> Create json-server folder in your computer(any locations)
--> Download this file: https://d18ky98rnyall9.cloudfront.net/_010a857c8cef22288ddc1db865c30e54_db.json?Expires=1500768000&Signature=b6Dn592CA5c-idrUl4s6qsi2LcNzP~P61MjSwfhK7yBZVM3F0jLH2awp376QGerZrOI5sjv0hosPPEegBtrwyC7pW0hqoAOOW-tlbr4vHP2kDU7vN-3tEXoYu7AMXO5HCirwORmH94KaWN8TTalA64saXJ3FM0q~vIwpgvS1Brc_&Key-Pair-Id=APKAJLTNE6QMUY6HBC5A and
    put db.json into json-server folder
--> Move to json-server folder through your terminal and run  json-server --watch db.json.It will start the server
--> In browser open localhost:3000


